title: Red Raiders split weekend series in Iowa - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Red Raiders split weekend series in Iowa - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: IOWA CITY, Iowa – The No. 17 Texas Tech baseball team's seven-game win streak came to an end on Sunday, falling to Iowa, 6-3, at Duane Banks Field. It was the Hawkeye's four-run sixth inning on this day that ultimately secured the weekend series split.
